h2. Social Helper

This is a simple helper for make more easy to publish on social networks.

h3. Installation

* Clone from github: in your helper directory type `git clone git@github.com:jlopezcur/SocialHelper.git`

OR

* Download directly from gitub into your helper directory.

h3. Available Social Networks

* Twitter (Publish link)
* Tuenti (Publish link)
* Google Plus (Publish link)

h3. Usage

# Add the following to the controller where you'd like to use the helper:
## var $helper = array('Social');
# In your view you can use the helper, for information about how to do this check the code in the Helper (is documented).

